a.n: One Day With Cesca Pey, Spain

p.k: This new episode of One day with shares with you the private life of one of our new Playboy TV Europe models: Cesca Pay, from Spain! Follow her morning routine relaxing in the shower and doing some shopping. She keeps in good shape exercising in the park and then show us the result of her efforts in a very hot photoshoot. There’s still time for a nice walk in the charming streets of Paris, where Cesca lives. So don’t miss anything from her everyday life!
